OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will
OL,6,Fremain mostly cloudy with some showery
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain, heavy at times,
OL,8,Fperhaps with thunder, along with some
OL,9,Fdrier periods. Freshening southerly
OL,10,Fbreeze in the east. Mild and humid.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FCloudy with outbreaks of
OL,13,Foccasionally heavy rain. Becoming
OL,14,Fdrier over northern abd western
OL,15,Fcounties in the afternoon with bright
OL,16,Fspells and a few showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
