OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FAny
OL,6,Fshowers clearing early Saturday to
OL,7,Fleave the rest of the weekend dry and
OL,8,Fbright, and becoming warm. Monday
OL,9,Fstaying dry with some sunshine, and
OL,10,Fbecoming very warm.
